<a href="http://growthhackjapan.com/2014-03-23-facebook-hack-released-to-the-public/" title="フェイスブックが独自のプログラミング言語「Hack」をオープンソース化" target="_self"><img src="http://growthhackjapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Screen-Shot-2014-03-23-at-12.25.06-363x263.png" alt="" border="0" width="363" height="263" class="wpp-thumbnail wpp_cached_thumb wpp_featured" /></a>
